== 影响和纪录 ==
飓风艾娃存在期间始终位于海上<ref name="Unisys map">{{cite web | deadurl = yes | publisher = Unisys | accessdate = 2015-06-09 | url = http://www.weather.unisys.com/hurricane/e_pacific/1973/AVA/track.gif | format = GIF | title = Hurricane AVA | archivedate = 2014-01-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140103204241/http://www.weather.unisys.com/hurricane/e_pacific/1973/AVA/track.gif }}</ref>，因此没有任何报道表明这场风暴造成人员丧生或破坏。不过，气旋达到热带风暴强度并获名“艾娃”（{{lang|en|Ava}}）后不久，有3艘船只测得的风速略低于[[烈风|烈风]]强度。<ref name="mwr" />此外，6月9至10日，风暴激起的大浪在[[南加州|南加州]]海岸产生危险的潮汐和强烈的离岸流。[[纽波特比奇_(加利福尼亚州)|纽波特比奇]]和[[长滩_(加利福尼亚州)|长滩]]的浪高分别达到2.7和1.8米，[[海豹滩_(加利福尼亚州)|海豹滩]]也有2.4米。大浪令沙滩变得更加危险，南加州各海滩的[[救生员|救生员]]队伍人数达到往常的2到3倍，海豹滩和纽波特比奇的救生员分别进行了35和75次救援。<ref name="Williams">{{cite news | publisher = The Hurricane Newspaper Archive | date = 1973-06-11 | work = Long Beach Independent | author = Tom Williams | page = A3 | title = 'Hurricane surf' hits Southland; lifeguards busy | place = Long Beach, California}}</ref>

飓风艾娃创下许多纪录，虽有多项已被打破，但任有少数维持至今。艾娃的五级飓风强度保持到1973年6月7日<ref name="EPAC HURDAT" />，此后要过7712天，才有[[1994年太平洋飓风季|1994年]]的[[1994年飓风艾米利亚|飓风艾米利亚]]于1994年7月19日达到五级强度<ref name="CPHC 1994">{{cite web | title = The 1994 Central Pacific Tropical Cyclone Season | accessdate = 2015-06-09 | publisher = Central Pacific Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2015-04-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150417220800/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/summaries/1994.php | deadurl = no | url = http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/summaries/1994.php }}</ref>。这一时间跨度之大，比有纪录以来世界上任何海域两场接续的五级飓风间隔时间都要长。1994年的[[1994年飓风吉尔玛|飓风吉尔玛]]于7月24日达到五级标准，又与飓风艾米利亚一起创下五级飓风间隔时间的最短纪录。<ref name="EPAC HURDAT" />艾娃在五级标准下保持了24小时，创下新纪录，但这一纪录之后由同样1994年的[[1994年飓风约翰|飓风约翰]]打破，此后[[1997年太平洋飓风季|1997年]]的[[1997年飓风琳达|飓风琳达]]和[[2006年飓风伊欧凯|飓风伊欧凯]]都超过了艾娃的纪录<ref name="E8">{{cite web | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/E8.html | author = Neal Dorst | title = Subject: E8) What hurricanes have been at Category Five status the longest? | date = 2004-08-13 | work = FAQ | accessdate = 2015-06-09 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150327065447/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/E8.html | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2015-03-27 }}</ref>。此外，飓风艾娃至今仍是[[赤道|赤道]]以北[[西半球|西半球]]在6月存在过的最强热带气旋<ref name="EPAC HURDAT" /><ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2015-05-07 | accessdate = 2015-06-09 | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | archivedate = 2015-05-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150510121046/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2014-050515.txt | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2014-050515.txt }}</ref>。

[[美国国家气象局|美国国家气象局]]发言人称：“艾娃处于最高强度时，其持续风速约有180[[节_(单位)|节]]，阵风时速达200节”（分别相当于每小时333.36公里和370.4公里）<ref name="Williams" />。但无论是官方发布的“最佳路径”（{{lang|en|Best track}}）数据，还是《[[每月天气回顾|每月天气回顾]]》上季度总结的数据都远远不及，认为这场飓风的最高风速为140节（相当于每小时259.28公里）<ref name="mwr" /><ref name="EPAC HURDAT" />。如果气旋风速真如这位发言人所言，那么艾娃就是有纪录以来地球上最强烈的热带气旋之一。但是，如此之高的风速本身就存在可疑。<ref name="E1">{{cite web | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/E8.html | title = Subject: E1) Which is the most intense tropical cyclone on record? | author = Chris Landsea | work = FAQ | date = 2006-11-28 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150327065447/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/E8.html | accessdate = 2015-06-09 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-03-27 }}</ref>

飓风艾娃915毫巴（百帕，27英寸汞柱）的最低气压也创下东北太平洋飓风的新纪录；此后虽先后被[[飓风琳达|飓风琳达]]、[[2009年飓风里克|里克]]、[[2002年飓风肯纳|肯纳]]和[[飓风帕特里夏|帕特里夏]]超越，但至今仍是史上第五强太平洋飓风<ref name="EPAC HURDAT" />。同时，琳达和里克的气压都是按卫星图像估算得出<ref name="Linda">{{cite web | title = Preliminary Report Hurricane Linda | date = 1997-10-25 | author = Max Mayfield | accessdate = 2015-06-09 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141102192752/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/1997linda.html | archivedate = 2014-11-02 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/1997linda.html }}</ref>，所以如只计测得气压，艾娃的纪录就要保持到2002年10月下旬才被肯纳超越<ref name="Kenna">{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2002kenna.shtml | title = Hurricane Kenna 2002 | author1 = Franklin, James L. | type = Tropical Cyclone Report | author2 = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140716085913/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2002kenna.shtml | accessdate = 2014-07-16 | date = 2002-12-26 | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2014-07-16 }}</ref>。不过，考虑到东北太平洋的地球同步卫星观测直到1966年才启动，所以此前的气象纪录可能不够可靠<ref name="Linda" />。艾娃的气压纪录本身也有欠完整，测得915毫巴气压时，风暴尚属四级强度，达到五级强度后唯一一次测得的气压值反而更高，有928毫巴（百帕，27.4英寸汞柱）<ref name="Unisys data">{{cite web | url = http://www.weather.unisys.com/hurricane/e_pacific/1973/AVA/track.dat | publisher = Unisys | title = Hurricane AVA | accessdate = 2015-06-09 | format = DAT | archivedate = 2013-11-13 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131113143242/http://weather.unisys.com/hurricane/e_pacific/1973/AVA/track.dat }}</ref>。这两项因素表明艾娃的实际最低气压可能低于915毫巴，也可能会有比艾娃更强烈的其它东太平洋气旋存在<ref name="Guillermo">{{cite web | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/1997guillerm.html | title = Preliminary Report Hurricane Guillermo | date = 1997-10-02 | author = Max Mayfield | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-06-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141112104305/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/1997guillerm.html | archivedate = 2014-11-12 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

